<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFHeath1921">Heath, Thomas (1921). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=LOA5AAAAMAAJ&amp;pg=PR323" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=LOA5AAAAMAAJ&amp;pg=PR323" rel="nofollow">A History of Greek Mathematics, Vol. 2</a></i>. Oxford: Clarendon Press. pp.&#160;323–324<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=LOA5AAAAMAAJ&amp;pg=PR323" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=LOA5AAAAMAAJ&amp;pg=PR323" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=LOA5AAAAMAAJ&amp;pg=PR323</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+History+of+Greek+Mathematics%2C+Vol.+2&amp;rft.aulast=Heath&amp;rft.aufirst=Thomas&amp;rft.au=Heath%2C+Thomas&amp;rft.date=1921&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B323%E2%80%93324&amp;rft.place=Oxford&amp;rft.pub=Clarendon+Press&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DLOA5AAAAMAAJ%26pg%3DPR323&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Hero_of_Alexandria"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
